with expected_protocol(ik.yokogawa.Yokogawa6370, [':FORMat:DATA REAL,64',
    ':SENS:WAV:STOP?', ':SENS:WAV:STOP {:e}'.format(value)], ['6.000000e-06']
    ) as inst:
    assert inst.stop_wl == 6e-06 * u.meter
    inst.stop_wl = value * u.meter
given(value=st.floats(min_value=6e-07, max_value=1.7e-06))
